N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 1646-7.3 - Letter of transmittal and certificate

State Regulations

Each quarterly financial statement shall be submitted
with a letter of transmittal and certificate listing the documents, data and
supporting schedules (by numbers) included therein. The form to be used is
shown as Exhibit 21 of Appendix S-11. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
1646-7.3

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
